title: Knitting - April 2016
description:
English | 100 pages | PDF | 26.7 MB

Knitting magazine offers all you need for the style-conscious knitter, whether you are a beginner, returner or an experienced knitter. Every issue is packed with exclusive knitting (and crochet) patterns for womens' fashionable garments and accessories, babies, children, men and the home plus tips from the experts, trend reports, designer profiles and fascinating features
